Croogo Eshop  plugin
------------------------------
Very simple eshop plugin for Croogo,
momentary without basket feature and orders evidence.
Only base items

How to install
------------------------------
- Log in to admin panel
- Go to Extensions > Plugins page
- Upload the zip file (available here)
- Click on tick/cross icon of 'Eshop' for activating or deactivating the plugin

Setting
------------------------------
List of all eshop suppliers in Extensions->Esho->Suppliers.
Min. one supplier required

How to use
------------------------------
Admin:
Your node must be of 'product' type. You can admin
eshop items by clicking on Eshop tab in Node edit page
Here you can add, modify or delete eshop items

Use:
All items are attached to 'product' node by plugin behavior,
so you can use it in your controllers or views in array 'EshopItems' in
node result data

Next steps
-------------------------------
- basket feature
- orders evidence
- agragators feeds
